<font color="#FF0000">ENTITLEMENT?</font><br>
<tt>Thu Jan  8 19:56:00 US/Eastern 1998
</tt><p>
An above post asked what qualifies or entitles one to comment on a subject.  We dwell too much on the qualification of the individual.  What entitles any of us to comment?<br><br>
It is the right of speech and free opinion that we hold so dear that entitles us to an opinion.  We ask for a free nation.  Let us continue to act like it means something.<br><br>
We are all entitled to comment.  On the other hand entitlement does not guarantee acceptance.  That in any society must be an earned privilege.<br><br>

<p><code>--   (SW) </code><p>


